<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5057967>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22–26. Forewings of: 22, Pholetesor rhygoplitoides Whitfield; 23, P. bedelliae (Viereck); 24, P. powelli Whitfield; 25, P. variabilis Whitfield; 26, P.viminetorum(Wesmael)." ;
